title: Madden NFL 09 (PS2) (NTSC) (Fabio5ilva)
description:
Madden NFL 09 (PS2)

Region: NTSC

Year: 2008

Twenty years as a dynasty of gaming, Madden NFL 09 aims to deliver the most immersive gameplay, the richest online offerings and the most comprehensive feature depth in the history of the franchise. This year's edition features a special Family Play mode with simplified controls and easier play-calling as well as new SuperSim mode, an improved Franchise scoring system, and a host of other gameplay tweaks and improvements.
